normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18714ecf05b2c18550ae356bd362265756ccb88","tid":254920,"uid":54734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"好撚憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有問食左飯未都係<br />\n都係啲冇營養嘅對話"},{"pid":"a447c038dd494929134045b2a02be16e6b831557","tid":254920,"uid":27793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:16:03.000Z","msg":"問人做緊乜<br />\n同你唔熟點解要話你知我做緊乜？<br />\n如果係好熟真係無問題<br />\n男版：我會一嘢答我打緊飛機/ 剪鼻毛<br />\n女版：我會一嘢答我發緊呆/ 同人傾緊是非<br />\n<br />\n其實問人做緊乜果班人既心態<br />\n你地可唔可以唔好咁厚臉皮<br />\n家陣同你好熟？<br />\n我要講我啲私人行動俾你知做乜9<br />\n唔熟如果做緊啲尷尬嘢又要作個答案呃你<br />\n呃人好辛苦你知唔知<br />\n應付你就更加辛苦"},{"pid":"11f58b1b715bee66c9ee8f825090bf263e885463","tid":254920,"uid":27793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>😊呢個emoji好狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無撚錯 狗公先用 呢個emoji<br />\n扮溫柔唔係咁扮 呢個😊emoji只會令人寒心/假到仆街"},{"pid":"6d996a573073c60fd3e191541913a6cedf401ea8","tid":254920,"uid":15960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>😊呢個emoji好狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無撚錯 狗公先用 呢個emoji<br />\n扮溫柔唔係咁扮 呢個😊emoji只會令人寒心/假到仆街</blockquote><br />\n做緊乜呀😊？<br />\n食左飯未呀😊？"},{"pid":"b8bbc54fd3b97a6009133a66278a00f999d08b8e","tid":254920,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有問食左飯未都係<br />\n都係啲冇營養嘅對話</blockquote><br />\n係 一見到呢句就會覺得連個人都好無營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"